pageContext.claim: “But I've become friendly with a lot of them and they've said -- they say we're two things. It's incredible what you've done with the economy. They always say that. They always say it no matter what. They say we have done the most incredible job, and they always start off by congratulating me.”
pageContext.analysis: Foreign leaders have not said this publicly, and there’s no evidence they’ve said it in private.
